defs.name: Opcode
defs.value:
pub enum Opcode {
    CMov,
    Load,
    Store,
    Add,
    Mul,
    Div,
    Nand,
    Halt,
    MapSegment,
    UnmapSegment,
    Output,
    Input,
    LoadProgram,
    LoadValue,
    Undefinied,
}
